cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

Class QueryEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine.QueryEngine

  • public class QueryEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    Supports the execution of Knowledge Graph queries. Queries are specified as Triples in N-Triple format with the special "?" identifier representing query or "wild card". All matching Triples known by the Knowledge Graph are printed to stdout, preceded by the query string.
    See Also:
    KnowledgeGraph

        Queries KnowledgeGraph with a single query string
